{"id":"280299e93c739488620fd488dcb846d1fb8c46d8528994890d1ae8febc037589","item_id":"1e7e77c55d:0","text":"可以为不同的面分配不同的 surface（表面）和 displacement（置换）。"}
{"id":"41f8b8d9305832af4bfca5adebc724fb5214af7a2291012c0303d32879a6391f","item_id":"1e7e77c55d:1","text":"设置 Group（组）"}
{"id":"1083a96b2a81ae45a7640b1f00edba371b01391c5126477494e78a4a903c054c","item_id":"1e7e77c55d:2","text":"要将选中的面加入一个 group（组）："}
{"id":"11e974f45b3860a1691e94056b0a7ebd05e7ae6bdf29111c958434efc82c8bac","item_id":"1e7e77c55d:3","text":"将选择模式切换为 primitives（图元）。"}
{"id":"81bb92d4110ab8b0027ee774ad8a8965df912c6c1e5bd5a7896deb8c83e5ca7b","item_id":"1e7e77c55d:4","text":"在 Viewport（视口）中选择这些面。"}
{"id":"ea0fa7c99163f4ebba0222663ee9fc7fe05b33c9d5fd1ebbd0abfdd1ea677e8c","item_id":"1e7e77c55d:5","text":"在 Viewport（视口）中"}
{"id":"d6ebbfa0bd02d5e7470a2b2e8d047435b469977e9e7a839144ab6455ba98a133","item_id":"1e7e77c55d:6","text":"，按 TAB 键并选择"}
{"id":"34ca0e76608842ff3e7d924a455a396a82f471052c15e3f2ed7f090ac702e5c1","item_id":"1e7e77c55d:7","text":"Group"}
{"id":"5c89ced8dd0b9ff6c88c1419068fba736bc800b67dfb5c609d15e8c7aee1c1c2","item_id":"1e7e77c55d:8","text":"以将这些面加入该 group（组）。"}
{"id":"5932e392c2e1cd16bdf33ab0ab543fa72940ef0881533391d62c0a28287ce81d","item_id":"1e7e77c55d:9","text":"将 Material 分配给 Groups（组）"}
{"id":"394ad457e01d9636e3fbc61306dc68b117fa18d3bf7d8dea99dd136cd04b6466","item_id":"1e7e77c55d:10","text":"添加一个"}
{"id":"616cb218a65b982f61fd738e24ebe00d5a2ae039c0d386fed975a51d51b772f8","item_id":"1e7e77c55d:11","text":"Material"}
{"id":"837c8a3d62bc6a0a02b12b86257f1b5c401e17e9a9008df115b93d2d7cad718e","item_id":"1e7e77c55d:13","text":"如果要同时分配 Bxdf 和 displacement shader，需要在 PxrMaterialBuilder 节点内部，把 surface shader 和 displacement shader 都连接到 collect_output。"}
{"id":"6a99a8513303229401c510c76fd8104ef8c54aad4cd3366d7abd23a769edc88e","item_id":"1e7e77c55d:14","text":"通过将 Material 设置为 collect vop（见上文）或 Bxdf，把你的 group（组）分配给该材质。"}
{"id": "cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8", "item_id": "1e7e77c55d:12", "text": "。"}
